msgid "Exiting on first failure"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/docs/getting_started/test-suite.rst:94
msgid ""
"Sometimes it is useful to be able to iteratively fix one test at a time.  In "
"this case the ``--failfast`` option can be used to exit the test runner "
"after the first failure."
msgstr ""

